data.description: NOW OFFERING $5K to help BUY DOWN YOUR INTEREST RATE or for closing cost!! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of central Florida! This magnificent 4-Bedroom, 3-full Bathrooms, BONUS Upstairs Den/Game Room, Separate Formal Dinning, Separate OFFICE area, with a 3-Car Garage - this gem of a home boasts over 3,200 SF of pure elegance and comfort. Situated in a picturesque gated community that offers a wide array of amenities, this home is the perfect blend of luxury and convenience.    As you walk through the front door, you'll be greeted by a bright and spacious open-concept living area, perfect for entertaining friends and family. The modern kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast bar that is sure to be the heart of your home.    The master suite is a private oasis, complete with a tranquil en-suite bathroom featuring a large soaking tub, a separate shower, and dual vanities. With three additional generously sized bedrooms, there's room for everyone!    One of the many highlights of this fantastic property is its incredible location. Centrally located between Tampa and Orlando, you'll enjoy easy access to I-4, putting you within minutes of all the excitement these vibrant cities have to offer. Plus, you'll appreciate the convenient proximity to a range of retail shopping, restaurants, grocery stores, schools, and medical facilities.    But the amenities within this gated community truly set it apart. Take a dip in the temperature-controlled pool, relax in the spa/hot tub, or challenge your neighbors to a friendly game of basketball, tennis, or pickleball. The clubhouse and meeting room are perfect for hosting events, while the covered playground and gazebo by the community lake provide endless opportunities for outdoor fun. And don't forget the gorgeous scenery that surrounds you, offering breathtaking views for your daily walks, jogs, or bike rides.    So, pack your bathing suits, sunscreen, and pickleball paddles and get ready to experience the lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Schedule your private showing today and start living your best life in this incredible home. Don't miss out on this opportunity – the Florida oasis you've been searching for awaits!
